{"tid":822163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台：山竹漸遠離香港　掛10號波維持數小時","createTime":"2018-09-16T08:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T12:42:24.000Z","uid":22349,"like":7,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"94677f036c195c2b450b952048c1ce8d79529ce1","tid":822163,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:00:22.000Z","msg":"【不斷更新】山竹漸遠離　掛10號波維持數小時<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180916/bkn-20180916011020932-0916_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180916%2Fbkn-20180916011020932-0916_00822_001.html&d=yzDWzY8%2F1k9pWZDPZiwDOhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=987d2337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180916/bkn-20180916011020932-0916_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n強颱風「山竹」逼近，香港今日(16日)天氣惡劣，10號風球現正懸掛。 <br />\n<br />\n【15:48】天文台指，山竹開始逐漸遠離香港，料會在黃昏前後在珠江口以西沿岸登陸。與山竹相關具破壞性的東南暴風至颶風仍影響香港，料10號颶風信號仍會維持數小時。"},{"pid":"00165d4987a63ffd5c0921e216aee27136f6aee2","tid":822163,"uid":15984,"like":86,"dislike":11,"score":75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:01:01.000Z","msg":"唔好貼上風撚Post<br />\n<br />\n實被屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c6ec700db9fd6879d9e27391a3a9d2fb1cb15a","tid":822163,"uid":54517,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00165d4987a63ffd5c0921e216aee27136f6aee2","tid":822163,"uid":15984,"like":86,"dislike":11,"score":75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:01:01.000Z","msg":"唔好貼上風撚Post<br />\n<br />\n實被屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj